definition: nature/character/property/quality/attribute/sexuality/sex/gender/suffix forming adjective from verb/suffix forming noun from adjective, corresponding to -ness or -ity/essence/CL:個|个[ge4]

sentences.english: Summary is the actual description of the event.
sentences.chinese: 總結是事件的實際性描述。

sentences.english: So what does that mean, in terms of practical advice?
sentences.chinese: 那麼就實際性的建議來說，這有什麼意義呢？

sentences.english: So big difference between actuality and possibility.
sentences.chinese: 實際性和可能性有很大不同。

sentences.english: There was also a practical element to Himmler's recruitment of foreign nationals .
sentences.chinese: 這也是希姆萊招募外籍士兵的一個很實際性的問題。
